It is also very strange that a band like yours will remain united and with the same members for so long.
Yes, four of us have been together for 21 years and Matt (Cameron) joined us 13 years ago, which, by itself, is much longer than many bands.
First of all, I think we are all fortunate to be still alive and, secondly, we all care about others.
